<item>
            <title>[SOLR-5009] CoreContainer instantiates 2 SolrResourceLoaders (implicit) but does not close all of them</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-5009</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Windows fails to delete files when they are open. CoreContainer opens a second SolrResourceLoader (implicit) when calling ConfigSolr.fromFile(). It should not do this and use the main loader, whcih is closed on shutdown.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This will remove the support for implicit ResourceLoader in ConfigSolr, preventing multiple classloaders for the same solr home.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
